{"word":"G38 - ἁγιασμός - hagiasmós - hag-ee-as-mos' - Holiness","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἁγιασμός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hagiasmós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hag-ee-as-mos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Holiness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பரிசுத்தம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"consecration, purification, the effect of consecration:sanctification of heart and life"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G37 - ἁγιάζω - hagiázō - hag-ee-ad'-zo/37\">G37</a>; properly <i>purification</i>, that is, (the state) <i>purity</i>; concretely (by Hebraism) a <i>purifier:</i> - holiness, sanctification."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G37 - ἁγιάζω - hagiázō - hag-ee-ad'-zo/37\">G37</a>, <a href=\"#/G38 - ἁγιασμός - hagiasmós - hag-ee-as-mos'/38\">G38</a>, <a href=\"#/G40 - ἅγιος - hágios - hag'-ee-os/40\">G40</a>, <a href=\"#/G41 - ἁγιότης - hagiótēs - hag-ee-ot'-ace/41\">G41</a>, <a href=\"#/G42 - ἁγιωσύνη - hagiōsýnē - hag-ee-o-soo'-nay/42\">G42</a>"}]}